paragraphs.title: Load data into table
paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.commons.io.IOUtils
import java.net.URL
import java.nio.charset.Charset

// Zeppelin creates and injects sc (SparkContext) and sqlContext (HiveContext or SqlContext)
// So you don't need create them manually

// load bank data
val airlineText = sc.parallelize(
    IOUtils.toString(
        new URL("https://s3.cn-north-1.amazonaws.com.cn/share-video-asiainfo/airline_data.csv"),
        Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))

case class Airline(search_date:String,
                   dep_date:String, 
                   company:String,
                   airline_num:String, 
                   start_airport:String, 
                   start_terminal:String, 
                   start_time:String,
                   arrive_airport:String,
                   arrive_terminal:String,
                   discount:String,
                   duration:String)
val airline = airlineText.map(s=>s.split(",")).map(
    s=>Airline(
           s(0).toString, 
           s(1).toString, 
            s(2).toString, 
            s(3).toString,
            s(4).toString, 
            s(5).toString, 
             s(6).toString,
             s(7).toString, 
             s(8).toString, 
             s(9).replaceAll("折", "").replaceAll("全价","10"), //discount
             s(10).toString //duration
        )
)

airline.toDF.registerTempTable("airline_data");

val airlinecircleText = sc.parallelize(
    IOUtils.toString(
        new URL("https://s3.cn-north-1.amazonaws.com.cn/share-video-asiainfo/airline_data_circle.csv"),
        Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))

case class Airlinecircle(rk:Int,
                   diff:Int, 
                   company:String,
                   airline_num:String, 
                   start_airport:String, 
                   start_city:String,
                   arrive_airport:String,
                   arrive_city:String,
                   arrive_subject:String,
                   discount:String,
                   start_time:String,
                   duration:String)
val airlinecircel = airlinecircleText.map(s=>s.split(',')).map(
    s=>Airlinecircle(
           s(0).toInt, 
           s(1).toInt, 
            s(2).toString, 
            s(3).toString,
            s(4).toString, 
             s(5).toString,
             s(6).toString, 
             s(7).toString, 
              s(8).toString,
             s(9).replaceAll("折", "").replaceAll("全价","10"), //discount
              s(10).toString, 
             s(11).toString //duration
        )
)

airlinecircel.toDF.registerTempTable("airline_data_circle");


//airline.filter(s=>s.marital == "married").toDF.registerTempTable("married");

//val tables = sqlContext.sql("show tables").collect.map(s=>s(0))
var company_airlines = sqlContext.sql("select id from (select  distinct concat(company,'|',airline_num) as id from airline_data) tab_id order by id ").collect.map(s=>s(0))
var city_list= sqlContext.sql("select  distinct start_city  from airline_data_circle ").collect.map(s=>s(0))
z.angularBind("selectedcompany_airlines", "四川航空|3U1005")
z.angularBind("company_airlines", company_airlines)
z.angularBind("inputdiscount",4.3)
z.angularBind("selectedcity","北京")
z.angularBind("selecteddate","2016-09-20")
z.angularBind("city_list",city_list)
z.angularBind("selectedcity1","北京")
z.angularBind("selectedcity2","广州")
z.angularBind("selectedcity3","北京")
z.angularBind("selectedcity4","广州")
z.angularBind("selecteddate2","2016-09-20")

var discount= z.angular("inputdiscount") var company_str= z.angular("selectedcompany_airlines").toString.split('|')(0) var airline_str= z.angular("selectedcompany_airlines").toString.split('|')(1) var stat = sqlContext.sql("select discount, case when "+discount+" =100 then '朋友 没有更深的坑了' when ( "+discount+" - discount)/(10-discount)*100 >=80 then 'lvegui' when ( "+discount+" - discount)/(10-discount)*100 >= 60 then '嗯 我只能说钱财身外物 坑的有点惨' when ( "+discount+" - discount)/(10-discount)*100 >=40 then '朋友 爬坑锻炼身体吧' when ( "+discount+" - discount)/(10-discount)*100 >=20 then '微微的小坑，下次就能躲过去喽' else '哇塞您很幸运哦，丁点没被坑' end end from (select cast(discount AS FLOAT) discount from airline_data where airline_num='"+airline_str+"' and company='"+ company_str +"') order by discount limit 1").collect var min_discount=stat(0)(0) println(min_discount) var width=stat(0)(1) var title=stat(0)(2) print(s""" %angular

$title 最低折:$min_discount

80%
""")
